#: ../../V/vulture-capitalist.rst:5
msgid "vulture capitalist"
msgstr "vulture capitalist"

#: ../../V/vulture-capitalist.rst:7
msgid "n\\."
msgstr "名詞"

#: ../../V/vulture-capitalist.rst:9
msgid ""
"Pejorative hackerism for ‘venture capitalist’, deriving from the common "
"practice of pushing contracts that deprive inventors of control over their "
"own innovations and most of the money they ought to have made from them."
msgstr ""
"‘venture "
"capitalist(ベンチャーキャピタリスト)’に対する軽蔑的なハッカー語。発明者から自らの革新に対する支配権と、本来得るべきだった金銭のほとんどを奪う契約を押し付ける一般的な慣行に由来する。"
